        <p>I’ve been married to my handsome, talented husband for over 5 years. We met when I started my postdoctoral fellowship in Baltimore, MD and it didn’t take long for us to know that we were meant for each other. During our years together, we have and continue to enjoy new cultural experiences with one another. We especially enjoy visiting wineries and museums and trying new ethnic cuisines. He’s my perfect partner in every way and my test subject for all of the new dishes I prepare.</p>
      </div>
