      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>As a scientist, I look at cooking much the same as I look at following a scientific protocol. Both have a set of ingredients that must be added at a particular time for the end product to turn out as expected. For me, cooking is a form of therapy and I love finding new and different recipes to prepare for my husband and I. I especially enjoy preparing dishes from different regions of the world as it exposes our palates to new and different flavors. Sometimes the meals turn out better than I expected. Other times, this isn’t the case. Either way, I’m learning as I go and finding new flavors that I never expected to enjoy.</p>
